{"tid":2300441,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"繼 嘉士伯 同 生力啤後 藍妹 都棄暗投明","createTime":"2020-11-25T13:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T14:07:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"363739cf025015e3e7e95aa1a6dfff99fa0b5c3f","tid":2300441,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"轉載：<br />\n<br />\n嘉士伯過檔，藍妹過檔，生力啤過檔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1UE0t4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1UE0t4.jpg&h=70f53c7b&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<blockquote>大家最近有無睇viu《男排女將》？其中一間贊助商就係藍妹！唔講大家未必知，其實藍妹上年仲用緊TVB張秀文做代言，但今年已經換晒viu班底，仲要係搵ERROR (大家起吓底就知咩料)，據知ERROR第一套MV，藍妹都係有份贊助嘅。所以，除咗嘉記之外，大家都可以考慮吓藍妹(捷成)啲啤酒架！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啤酒廣告就好誠實嘅，CCTVB一個啤酒廣告都無，即係證明無後生會睇，跟住落嚟就係要教班師奶轉睇viutv同netflix，同派<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">留言多謝藍妹</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"pink\">❤️ Blue Girl 藍妹 ❤️</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/242130779133990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F242130779133990&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=8f9fe0be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/242130779133990</a></p><br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">感謝 貴公司與TVB割蓆、在其他電視台投放廣告，以及使用viu藝人宣傳產品，本人承諾日後將會購買藍妹及其他捷成的啤酒，以作答謝❤️</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEPmuBA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEPmuBA.png&h=38244090&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"d90a272804448cdfe93cca0b9977cc8f10a9575f","tid":2300441,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">💚 捷成啤酒包括：藍妹、Beck's、Corona、Hoegaarden、Stella、百威、森堡、盧雲堡、三得利等</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jebsenbeer.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jebsenbeer.com%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=fe559247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.jebsenbeer.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\"><strong>常見問題1：之前唔係話藍妹喺CCTVB有廣告咩？</strong></span><br />\n常見答案1：今年的確有套劇集《殺手》係由藍妹提供產品贊助，但套劇係2018年拍。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>常見問題2：我見到藍妹有搵微辣拍廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n常見答案2：微辣成員有黃有藍喇，表過態嗰幾位咪黃(起碼唔係藍先)，上央視晚會唱歌嗰啲咪藍/紅囉。如果你真係唔鍾意，你可以留言話「多謝你同TVB割蓆呀，我好鍾意睇ERROR，不過就唔鍾意睇XXX！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">【TVB戰線懶人區】(最後更新25 Nov 2110)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【紅媒金主】雅窗牌、匡橋 (24 Nov)<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/1542434506031343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F1542434506031343&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=357ac97d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/1542434506031343</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/2325001171058388\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F2325001171058388&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=8fd357e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/2325001171058388</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299079</a><br />\n<br />\n【紅媒金主】立邦油漆 (23 Nov)<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/298174674531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F298174674531